      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was used without formal model form assessment. No comparison to alternative hemolysis models (e.g., Arora, Taskin) was performed. Model form uncertainty is unquantified and represents a critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
